<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٨٤٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">قُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4822">عَمْرٍو </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1091">جَابِرٍ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كُنَّا يَوْمَ الْحُدَيْبِيَةِ أَلْفًا وَأَرْبَعَمِائَةٍ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>